(1, 'Press Hostel',76,'PLN','kayak.com','Smocza 27, 01-048 Warszawa',4.2,'507 807 232','Press Hostel was created with passion for traveling and meeting new, interesting people. Our mission is to introduce visitors to Warsaw – present one and the one from the past. You can start with museums and other typical attractions reccommended by a guidebook, go with us to a club party.','https://presshostel.com/en/','52.2494087','20.98221','https://www.kayak.pl/rimg/himg/fe/30/c9/arbisoftimages-3184350-press-hostel-hotel-warszawa-012-image.jpg?width=1280&height=856&crop=true&caller=HotelInlineCarousel','https://www.kayak.pl/rimg/himg/fe/30/c9/arbisoftimages-3184350-press-hostel-hotel-warszawa-011-image.jpg?width=1280&height=856&crop=true&caller=HotelInlineCarousel','https://thumbnails.trvl-media.com/JgbPzRdlCGSyOsdqh6EdURI-spE=/773x530/smart/filters:quality(60)/exp.cdn-hotels.com/hotels/20000000/19790000/19782600/19782599/9c593962_z.jpg ','https://s-ec.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/320x400/121213016.jpg?k=e29c68e2438b5934f4b1dd5ea8d110a002f6e43d8ff0439d16af1d527b7ae6cc&o=','Hostel'),
(2, 'Museum Hotel',46,'EUR','booking.com','Mpoumpoulinas 16, Athina 106 82,',4.1,'+30 21 0380 5611','Athens Museum Hotel is a contemporary Athens city hotel located. next to the Athens Archaeological Museum and the Polytechnic University','https://presshostel.com/en/','37.988117','23.733336','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNuDLvDiP9WPY4khakNPQXXdlWDHsP6Uqc2cAtr=w592-h404-n-k-no-v1-rj','https://cdn.webhotelier.net/photos/w=1920/bstwmuseum/L193889.jpg','https://s-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/423/4230122.jpg','https://r-cf.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/789/7896350.jpg','Hotel'),
(3, 'Hotel Stanford - New York',140,'USD','booking.com','43 W 32nd St, New York, NY 10001,',4.0,'+1 212-563-1500','Hotel Stanford group is a collection of family-owned and operated boutique hotels, each with its own unique style and exciting location. A distinguished vision of old world charm and contemporary convenience, Hotel Stanford group strives to establish an internationally recognized brand for our affordability and captivating hospitality rooted in the values of the Orient.','http://www.hotelstanford.com/about-us-en.html','40.7482035','-73.9874565ho','https://s-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1024x768/195/195699810.jpg','https://res.cloudinary.com/lastminute/image/upload/c_scale,w_630/q_auto/v1490902875/Executive_Suite-5_wbfvbv.jpg','https://t-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max1280x900/711/7111104.jpg','https://q-xx.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/102/102112562.jpg','Hotel'),
(4, 'Hotel Budapest',41,'EUR','booking.com','Budapest, Szilágyi Erzsébet fasor 47',3.6,'+36 1 889 4200','Hotel Budapest – formerly called Round Hotel – caused a major stir as soon as it was built. The high-rise circular building full of windows was considered an architectural oddball, and so in time became one of the symbols of Budapest and a favourite with visitors. With its 15 stories and 64 metres in height, it’s still the tallest hotel in the country. From its higher floors, you get a breathtaking panoramic view of the various landmarks of the Buda and Pest sides of the city. The hotel, located in green surroundings at the foot of the Buda hills, is an excellent choice whether you want to go sightseeing, or you’ve come for a professional event, or if you want to go for a walk in the Buda hills: the buses or trams stopping in front of the hotel will take you to the M2 metro in Széll Kálmán Square in a few minutes, and also to many nice place in Buda, without having to change. The cog-wheel railway, a major tourist attraction in itself, stops right opposite the hotel, offering easy access to the Buda hills. The nearby Városmajor park is a great place for long walks, jogging and other outdoor exercise. ','www.danubiushotels.com','47.5102636','18.943081','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/15/86/e1/86/hotel-entrance.jpg','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/09/0c/02/62/corinthia-hotel-budapest.jpg','https://www.corinthia.com/application/files/6714/8396/8956/Exe-king-room.jpg','https://media.kempinski.com/34367372/bathroom-premium-room-kempinski-hotel-budapest.jpg;width=1905;height=794;mode=crop;anchor=middlecenter;autorotate=true;quality=75;scale=both;progressive=true;encoder=freeimage;format=jpg','Hotel'),
(5, 'Radisson Blu Seaside Hotel',86,'EUR','tripadvisor.com','Ruoholahdenranta 3, 00180 Helsinki,',4.2,'+358 20 1234707','Enjoy our comfortable rooms and suites boasting urban design and the Blu Dreams® sleeping experience, with modern amenities such as Free high-speed wireless Internet. The first ever Double King Rooms in Finland will add new and luxurious comfort for families and friendship alike and our two-storied lofts offer big-city atmospheres and magnificent views of the harbor. For movie fans we have now special Movie and Entertainment Rooms. These rooms have been designed to provide unparalleled comfort, entertainment and media access during your stay. Your favorite furry companion is welcomed to Seaside. Pet friendly rooms are available upon request for an additional fee. For food and drink stop by our recently opened Bistro Gimis for a distinctly Helsinki dining experience with fresh seafood as well as local dishes. ','https://www.radissonhotels.com','60.1619361','24.9247062','https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/18/e1/16/f0/exterior.jpg','https://thumbnails.trvl-media.com/bxTDB_wOTcJg7Rss0DnH7gjsXvI=/773x530/smart/filters:quality(60)/images.trvl-media.com/hotels/1000000/20000/16400/16398/dcf87fab_z.jpg','https://www.oyster.com/uploads/sites/35/2019/05/lobby-v14962614-1440-1024x683.jpg','https://tropki.com/images/hotels/b206008206/page/helsinki-radisson-blu-seaside-hotel-helsinki-4.jpg','Hotel');
